sentences.sentence: The same myth also applies to inbreed animals, who are not always the weaker of the species.
sentences.translation: 同样的谣传也适用于同系繁殖的动物，当然它们在种族中也并不是较弱的。

sentences.sentence: The morphology of anatomy and histology of vertebra and rib, and vertical compression on lumbar vertebrae in inbreed line Banna mining were studied.
sentences.translation: 本研究观察了版纳小型猪近交系椎骨、肋骨的解剖学、组织学形态，并对其腰椎进行轴向载荷压缩试验。

sentences.sentence: The morphology of anatomy and histology of vertebra and rib, and vertical compression on lumbar vertebrae in inbreed line Banna minipig were studied.
sentences.translation: 本研究观察了版纳小型猪近交系椎骨、肋骨的解剖学、组织学形态，并对其腰椎进行轴向载荷压缩试验。
